data.description: Looking for an affordable and well maintained home in Moss Bluff? Look no further; this recently renovated home has so much to offer. This beautiful property offers 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths sitting on .65 acres. Completely fenced in yard with exterior shed that has access to electricity and an oversized patio. All inspections have been completed on this property and all repairs have been made. This property is move in ready!! Schedule your showing today! THIS HOME QUALIFIES FOR 100% FINANCING! BACK ON THE MARKET AT NO FAULT OF SELLER NOR PROPERTY.
